  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to establish the effect of ET blockade on the acute exercise
      induced blood flow and endothelial function in subjects with T2DM. We hypothesize that
      combining ET - blockade with exercise training leads to an acute increase of exercise induced
      blood flow when compared with exercise alone. We expect that this will lead to an
      optimization of vascular training effect in T2DM.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
